{"first_name":"Jack","last_name":"Smith","permalink":"jack-smith-3","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/person/jack-smith-3","homepage_url":"","birthplace":"Kentucky","twitter_username":"jkellonsmith","blog_url":"","blog_feed_url":"","affiliation_name":"WPP","born_year":null,"born_month":null,"born_day":null,"tag_list":"wpp, 247-real-media, social-media, digital-advertising, ad-serving, technology, search-engine-marketing","alias_list":null,"created_at":"Thu Aug 05 17:33:08 UTC 2010","updated_at":"Tue Jan 10 07:37:23 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Jack is the Chief Product Officer at Simulmedia. One of world’s leading digital advertising visionaries, Jack was the founder of Solariat, a venture backed company that uses artificial intelligence for social media marketing and analysis. Previously, Jack founded and ran the MIG (now Xaxis) for WPP Group, the world’s largest communications services company. \nAt the MIG, he created ZAP &amp; B3 to help agencies and advertisers improve the process of planning, buying, trafficking and optimizing digital media advertising campaigns. Prior to The MIG, Jack was SVP, Product Strategy at 24/7 Real Media, a leading provider of digital advertising technologies and services and now a unit of WPP.</p>\n\n<p>Jack is also a veteran of The Hearst Corporation, where he was Director of Operations for the WISN Division responsible for the operation of two radio stations. He serves on the National Advisory Board of the University of Kentucky College of Communications and Information Studies. He lives in New York with his wife, two daughters and large hound dog.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,150],"assets/images/resized/0016/9044/169044v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[250,250],"assets/images/resized/0016/9044/169044v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[450,450],"assets/images/resized/0016/9044/169044v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":"<p>Simulmedia</p>"},"degrees":[],"relationships":[{"is_past":false,"title":"Chief Product Officer","firm":{"name":"Simulme